data.text: @AgonyFrankErnie @enews There is always a balance to life huh, it now takes you less time to dry your hair but more time to wash your face. Our secret recipes could change the world if the world would let us huh.

@UncleEarnest @enews Everything happens for a reason as we both know. The baldness took 10 seconds off my 50m butterfly. Perhaps we can let new friends know that our patented depilation can help in various situations where hair is an unexpected or unwelcome dinner guest. Tweet us for more details!
@UncleEarnest @enews We live in a world of wonders good friend. Last time I left stuff on my hair I went bald.
@enews Hey @AgonyFrankErnie if only people paid this much attention to inner maintenance we could’ve retired a lot sooner huh good buddy? Huh huh huh 🤪🤩🧐
